 \u201cMay Allah have mercy on the one who shows me my faults.\u201d Source: Sunan al-Da\u0304rimi\u0304 649 \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0639\u064e\u0628\u0651\u064e\u0627\u062f\u0650 \u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u0639\u064e\u0628\u0651\u064e\u0627\u062f\u064d \u0627\u0644\u0652\u062e\u064e\u0648\u0651\u064e\u0627\u0635\u0650 \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0639\u064f\u0645\u064e\u0631\u064f \u0628\u0652\u0646\u064f \u0627\u0644\u0652\u062e\u064e\u0637\u0651\u064e\u0627\u0628\u0650 \u0631\u064e\u0636\u0650\u064a\u064e \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0647\u064f \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652\u0647\u064f \u0631\u064e\u062d\u0650\u0645\u064e \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0647\u064f \u0645\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u064e\u0647\u0652\u062f\u064e\u0649 \u0625\u0650\u0644\u064e\u064a\u0651\u064e \u0639\u064f\u064a\u064f\u0648\u0628\u0650\u064a 649\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":26014,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2018\/03\/04\/big-belly-punishment-not-blessing\/","url_meta":{"origin":6640,"position":2},"title":"Umar on Gluttony: A large belly is a punishment, not a blessing","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"March 4, 2018","format":false,"excerpt":"Al-Hasan reported: Umar ibn al-Khattab, may Allah be pleased with him, saw a man with a large belly and he said, \u201cWhat is this?\u201d The man said, \u201cIt is a blessing from Allah.\u201d Umar said, \u201cNo, rather it is a punishment.\u201d Source: H\u0323adi\u0304th Muh\u0323ammad ibn \u2018Abd Alla\u0304h al-Ans\u0323a\u0304ri\u0304 42 \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0650\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":43710,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2025\/05\/15\/best-ummah-abu-bakr\/","url_meta":{"origin":6640,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Caliphs: Best of Ummah are Abu Bakr, Umar, and Uthman","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"May 15, 2025","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Umar reported: In the lifetime of the Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, while his companions were numerous, we preferred Abu Bakr, Umar, and Uthman, then we would remain silent. Source: Musnad Ah\u0323mad 4626 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Arna\u2019ut Imam Ahmad commented, \u201cThe best of\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":33887,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2020\/01\/06\/condemnation-nikah-halala\/","url_meta":{"origin":6640,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Marriage: Condemnation of Nikah Halala","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"January 6, 2020","format":false,"excerpt":"Abdullah ibn Mas'ud reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, cursed the one who marries a woman to overturn an irrevocable divorce and the man for whom it is done. Al-Tirmidhi said, \"This tradition was acted upon by the people of knowledge among the companions of\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":33931,"ur